{"word":"G5517 - χοϊκός - choïkós - kho-ik-os' - Earthy","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χοϊκός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">choïkós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kho-ik-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Earthy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மண்ணான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"made of earth, earthy"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5522 - χόος - chóos - kho'-os/5522\">G5522</a>; <i>dusty</i> or <i>dirty</i> (<i>soil</i> like), that is, (by implication) <i>terrene:</i> - earthy.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}